Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚门上等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们至今所耗费的时间究竟有什么意义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我甚至不能去憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那根本是无路可走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪儿都去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能去任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你都还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是生命还在 徒增空虚罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说空虚也是一种感情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是确实存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我去感受?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回可别再躲开了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据第三据点的情报显示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白鸽盯上了这前面的喰种组织
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的想法我也懂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但想救出所有喰种是不可能的啊 王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太残忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来地上再也不是我们的安生之所了
Comment: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:00.14,OP,,0,0,0,,/----OP----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:06.22,OP,,0,0,0,,例えば目が覚めて「すべては幻だ」って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:12.39,OP,,0,0,0,,奇跡めいた妄想を叶えて欲しいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:19.12,OP,,0,0,0,,僕が描いた罪で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:25.76,OP,,0,0,0,,結末を満たさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:39.64,OP,,0,0,0,,壊し続けた僕は何かを救えた？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:45.70,OP,,0,0,0,,変わり果てた今に革命のナイフ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:49.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}ほどけるように刺して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:53.77,OP,,0,0,0,,光に満ちたさよならを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:57.37,OP,,0,0,0,,I will miss you, I will miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:00.70,OP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}罰を僕に与えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:07.43,OP,,0,0,0,,君はまだ僕を愛してはくれるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:13.66,OP,,0,0,0,,「僕じゃなきゃ」「僕じゃダメだ」「僕じゃなきゃ」がループする
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:20.01,OP,,0,0,0,,僕を刺したナイフさえも  いつかきっと光を射すから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:06.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,希望某天醒来 发现一切都是幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:12.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我多想这种奇迹般的妄想能成为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:19.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,不要让我的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:25.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,成为故事的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:39.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,破坏众多存在的我 又拯救了什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:45.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,给面目全非的如今 一场革命的刀光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:49.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}仿佛要彻底获得解脱一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:53.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,渴求那个充满光明的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:00.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}给我应有的惩罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:07.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,你仍旧愿意爱我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:13.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,陷入「非我不可」「我不行的」「非我不可」的循环
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:20.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,刺向我的刀光 迟早也会毁灭那片光明
Comment: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,/----07-----
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是处男?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:40.62,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1A1A1A&\be0.5\fs100\fsp25\pos(985,230)}牵绊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我问你是不是处男
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 只是觉得大概是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得已时我让你上...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上...你的意思是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会放任他们自由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要驱逐所有喰种
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造一个没有错误的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是第三据点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须尽快移动到24区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,董香?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绚都已经赶去24区了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在还是会有其他据点被...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又打算一个人背负起全部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四方先生也在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有锦 月山 和青桐的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微依靠一下同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都在思考 怎样才能让你不离开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为你消失了也无所谓的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的话难道也是为这种理由...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种理由?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你成了白鸽那时 偶尔会一个人到店里来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻开书本 视线偷偷看着我这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经见过你那种眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你看利世的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就像个笨蛋一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对此感到开心的我 更像个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 请你回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是我能做的 不管任何事我都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家店充满了喰种的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的背叛了我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CCG  Qs  还有我...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说都算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师你失去了理智
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来为你驱除碍事的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 是老师的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昆克里有抑制剂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个没礼貌的客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧 偷腥猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 你这家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了她 杀了她 杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃屋特等 局长找你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要翘掉不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一起怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那时同样的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20区和枭的那一战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时也付出了很多流血
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平究竟是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类 喰种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要其中之一从世上消失 就能叫「和平」了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是认为 只要现在的生活能持续下去就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 黑磐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚礼 邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:49.62,IN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I dreamed you were beside me, you were there once again, as if you had never left and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:10:05.95,IN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I remember wanting to say, asking you not to go, but I know that was impossible then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:15.42,IN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You say "I can stay here" as my damp eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:37.75,IN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The sunshines on the bleak horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:42.88,IN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's just another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:52.82,IN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I look out at the dimly lit buildings and think of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:11:00.06,IN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And I imaging you here, right next to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:17.44,IN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Your eyes catch my own, I look back fleetingly, before I realize you're really there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:25.68,IN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I dreamed you'd be beside me, that we would meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:30.20,IN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Your eyes glisten, your tears are falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:45.75,IN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I know you have not forgotten the past that we shared as I quietly watch you wipe your tears away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:55.15,IN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Although I've found you, I know this meeting will not last.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:12:04.11,IN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I have to let go continue finding your way, though I miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:10.64,IN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's time to wake from this dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是爸爸妈妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的珍宝 现在送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到这个就会想起董香的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回24区吧 大家都在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道什么了吗 系璃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别小看了我的情报网
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑山羊在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,24区?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会就这么毁灭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢 不过...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能亲眼看到他们毁灭的瞬间 不是很美妙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就在特等席上好好欣赏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戏剧的落幕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真优秀啊 局长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过奖了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是和修一直以来都在放水罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要为这场小纠纷一样的游戏画上句号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离宣告胜利还需要什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足以让沉溺在和平中的废物全都吓尿的残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是最终Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是对喰种而言的吗 还是对CCG而言的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「那」将是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会创造最强的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把芳村爱支和有马贵将都秒杀的最强之「龙」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您找我吗 局长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑磐武臣 今天我有点事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前 我们先来复习一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喰种对策法八十八条第一项
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对藏匿喰种隐瞒不报者 将进行重罚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视情况甚至可以处以极刑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请记住这点 跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:34.83,Comments,,0,0,0,,24区\N黑山羊据点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓜江
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子学生时代的挚友 被发现是喰种
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子说她不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并没有证据能够证明她的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CCG的动向如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼了命在找王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们认为杀了领导者是最快的捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我们也得摧毁他们的领导者才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不打算就这么闷死在地底下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟还有孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:17:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 刚才的当我没说 忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,董香 董香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是那样 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体方面 有哪里不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来最近...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚经常抽筋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很困
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发有点乱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀孕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还不知道能不能顺利生下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想等确定以后再跟你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来不打算说的 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候出生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,董香 喰种是怎么结婚的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然问这个干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道喰种的世界是怎么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今都无所谓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都做了 而且我也有点不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会留下证明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证明?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 互相在对方的身体上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:19:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量重一些 留下至死都不会消失的咬痕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想救她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子小姐是武臣的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会给我们做美味面包的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然那是局长的决定我们就只能服从
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就一点感觉都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事已至此 结论不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个废柴男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肌肉练多了 连脑子都不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想看到黑磐那副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种地方我不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去当家里蹲...不 去当恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米林
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CCG就是个杀人组织 才子不想待在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米林
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很清楚这是无可奈何的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿瓜 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CCG确实已经疯狂了 大家都迷失了战斗的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都麻木了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得对 或许我们是该提出自己的意见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想在事后被当成罪犯来看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可要怎么做...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去当个恐怖分子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起跳舞到天明吧 阿锦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我 醉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害 没想到地底下还能举办婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是月山先生说该办一办 所以加急为我们准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些方面倒是很严谨啊 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好了吧
